{"tid":1453434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【終整文宣】分化深藍，拉攏淺藍，叫醒中立，鞏固淺黃","createTime":"2019-08-12T04:12:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:27:04.000Z","uid":305449,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"8ae2eeb4093862f42a1da29eff91b490b4230502","tid":1453434,"uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:12:19.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一貼<br />\n係到打飛機冇用，唔好等輸，唔該有時間就出去文宣洗版，根據政治取向唔同就用唔同既材料<br />\n民意未必係最重要，但係要升級，要成功，就一定要有足夠民意支持<br />\n<br />\n以下拋磚引玉，手機垃圾P圖，<strong>文宣必須要有針對性</strong>，唔可以用同一張圖或同一件事黎文宣比唔同政見既人，否則必定失敗！<br />\n<br />\n深藍冇可能拉到，就分化，難度頗高但係要努力<br />\nE.g.分化政府同警察，分化黑警同警察，深藍大多冇腦，所有野都唔需要fact check, 有幾誇張得幾誇張(各位巴打開始表演) <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tmqQuMx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtmqQuMx.jpg&h=a975dd70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9GLg9Mx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9GLg9Mx.jpg&h=18c82692&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n淺藍救得一個得一個，多一個隊友總好過多一個敵人<br />\nE.g. 話佢地知黑警濫暴有幾嚴重，或者插政府無能，淺藍只係比民建聯等賣港派洗腦，未必蠢，必須fact check<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bY2Wqke.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbY2Wqke.jpg&h=4033fdf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hXO0Tz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hXO0Tz.jpg&h=01d4d8de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tg3uLq2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTg3uLq2.jpg&h=50ed52a5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n中立仲未識醒既就叫醒佢地<br />\nE.g. 經濟牌，健康牌，最好燒到佢地痛處 <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LOnbYFw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLOnbYFw.jpg&h=23c849f3&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZudKzdR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudKzdR.jpg&h=2e8392d7&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YtwL27c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYtwL27c.jpg&h=521c2d02&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n淺黃既支持係絕對唔可以少得，鞏固淺黃支持係必須<br />\nE.g. 話佢地知點解唔可以割席，點解一定要贏<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Km4JPNb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKm4JPNb.jpg&h=0ca277ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0Np527u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0Np527u.jpg&h=06926b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n深黃基本上唔需要文宣，用時間黎討論行動好過<br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！要贏就要所有人一齊努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"fe7d7b9792bc2efe12eb474284793cfdb822329b","tid":1453434,"uid":285899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:16:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"940a13363c881fe67c2d59168132c2b0f3b58466","tid":1453434,"uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:39:07.000Z","msg":"正經野唔該推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b34d62a28d345c51ad12061dc79b80f0cf5e738","tid":1453434,"uid":29695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"唯一一個意見<br />\n隻曱甴可唔可以細隻啲，好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8b0ed8517de93c845c371aa1f632506d4871499","tid":1453434,"uid":305449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b34d62a28d345c51ad12061dc79b80f0cf5e738","tid":1453434,"uid":29695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:43:51.000Z","msg":"唯一一個意見<br />\n隻曱甴可唔可以細隻啲，好核突<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:47:02.000Z","msg":"P圖新手，sor"},{"pid":"e907f3301efa971cc5350d6f6a94a85aaff2f0c1","tid":1453434,"uid":15696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:47:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttLEooS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttLEooS.png&h=4b443cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vxZmxjw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvxZmxjw.png&h=1d33d451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g1fEi4i.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg1fEi4i.png&h=ea27d434&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ca31c45a155ffffc7ca12c48a7785fe1a7882705","tid":1453434,"uid":48679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T04:47:36.000Z","msg":"30000<br />\n29999<br />\n29998<br />\n29997<br />\n...<br />\n0"},{"pid":"28d1f7531b8a007fa0b0da8f69aebc841df28a9f","tid":1453434,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"大家可唔可以整多少少人神共憤嘅俾遊客<br />\n好多時佢地知 Hong Kong fight for freedom<br />\n但好多時吸睛嘅係<span style=\"color: red;\">殘忍同無恥嘅行為</span><br />\n同埋可以出<span style=\"color: red;\">數字</span><br />\n吸引左佢地再講其他野<br />\n要令佢地覺得我地起<span style=\"color: red;\">人道災難</span>入面<br />\n佢地係於心不忍 而唔係其他國家嘅野唔關佢地事<br />\n<br />\n文宣小妹有野想講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1451498\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1451498</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">721元朗恐襲</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6q9avh8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6q9avh8.jpg&h=33d6c51d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qsq1BYb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQsq1BYb.jpg&h=68ff5048&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mKPxJDg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmKPxJDg.jpg&h=9c8fe0d8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r1a1BYj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr1a1BYj.jpg&h=dbd6dfe2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z8jqjbJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ8jqjbJ.jpg&h=0c3c7178&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfBL3Ds.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfBL3Ds.jpg&h=00f1432c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Keut1qa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKeut1qa.jpg&h=c65958a9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/47P53Dy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F47P53Dy.jpg&h=4b2dc8d9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NPTRZbV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNPTRZbV.jpg&h=865361ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kohzcwX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkohzcwX.jpg&h=a5dae6ea&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}